If set to draft, the Wallet Class can only be seen by trusted testers.
Setting this field to underReview signals that the class is ready for review. An underReview class has the same visibility as a draft class, but will be sent to a Google team for approval. If the class is approved, this field is set to approved and the class will be visible to the public. If the class is rejected, this field is set to rejected and the class will not be visible to the public.
